183
00:11:25,920 --> 00:11:27,360
Yes.

184
00:11:27,480 --> 00:11:28,880
Do you understand?

185
00:11:29,360 --> 00:11:30,880
Yes.

186
00:11:38,160 --> 00:11:39,680
