195
00:12:05,960 --> 00:12:09,400
and cooperation between seniors and juniors.

196
00:12:10,320 --> 00:12:11,520
But to me

197
00:12:11,680 --> 00:12:14,480
we come to the university to study

198
00:12:14,520 --> 00:12:17,520
