594
00:36:30,280 --> 00:36:31,160
I am.

595
00:36:31,240 --> 00:36:32,520
The gold color is catching my eyes

596
00:36:32,640 --> 00:36:33,520
Is it pretty?

597
00:36:33,800 --> 00:36:35,200
And it’s rose gold, right?

598
00:36:35,320 --> 00:36:36,400
Yes.

599
00:36:37,400 --> 00:36:38,320
It’s the latest edition.

600
00:36:38,720 --> 00:36:40,320
Let me have the honor to touch it.

601
00:36:40,520 --> 00:36:41,520
There

602
00:36:41,680 --> 00:36:42,360
It’s pretty, right?

603
00:36:42,480 --> 00:36:42,960
Arthit.

604
00:36:43,080 --> 00:36:44,080
Look.

605
00:36:46,320 --> 00:36:47,520
This is rose gold.

606
00:36:47,840 --> 00:36:48,640
You know what?

607
00:36:48,800 --> 00:36:52,160
