608
00:36:53,280 --> 00:36:54,360
Take a close look.

609
00:36:56,200 --> 00:36:57,320
You can touch it.

610
00:36:57,400 --> 00:36:59,520
Don’t worry. She’s kind.

611
00:37:07,480 --> 00:37:10,280
