614
00:37:14,000 --> 00:37:15,120
See you again later.

615
00:37:15,240 --> 00:37:16,440
I’ll contact back shortly.

616
00:37:16,600 --> 00:37:17,520
Okay. See you

617
00:37:17,800 --> 00:37:19,480
Bye bye. See you later.

618
00:37:23,360 --> 00:37:24,080
Arthit,

619
00:37:24,480 --> 00:37:25,840
hold these

