00:37:47,480 --> 00:37:49,120
Is there anything you want from me?

624
00:37:50,080 --> 00:37:51,720
If it’s about that flag capturing event,

625
00:37:52,000 --> 00:37:53,760
Khun Khongpob already talked to me.

626
00:37:55,680 --> 00:37:56,680
no.

627
00:37:57,320 --> 00:37:59,040
That’s not what I’m here for.

628
00:37:59,320 --> 00:38:01,240
I have another thing to talk to you.

629
00:38:05,640 --> 00:38:07,040
I’m curious

630
00:38:07,200 --> 00:38:09,480
why you have to go against the activity

631
00:38:09,520 --> 00:38:12,080
and isolate yourself to be here alone.

632
00:38:15,120 --> 00:38:16,920
