636
00:38:24,480 --> 00:38:26,880
But you don’t have to oppose it

637
00:38:30,160 --> 00:38:32,760
I don’t think that’s the real problem

638
00:38:34,200 --> 00:38:36,640
Did you have problems with your old university?

639
00:38:39,200 --> 00:38:40,720
What do you mean?

640
00:38:40,840 --> 00:38:42,960
That’s why you transfer to study here

641
00:38:43,200 --> 00:38:44,080
Am I right?

642
00:38:46,720 --> 00:38:48,520
That’s none of your business.

643
00:38:49,160 --> 00:38:51,800
